channel.title: Hal-get-property not found error on linux
channel.description: hi, I'm just trying to run main.py script from your's github (https://github.com/KeyAuth/KeyAuth-Python-Example) on Kali Linux 2022.2 and after input licence key I got error `hal-get-property not found` . I was trying to search some resolution but I found out hal is no more supported by Linuxes. On windows all is working great but is there any way to use it on Linux (Debian/Ubuntu)?
